Package: jwdid
Title: Extended Two-Way Fixed Effects Difference-in-Differences
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Yuki", "Matsuura", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "matsuura.yuki.200095@gmail.com")
Author: Yuki Matsuura [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Yuki Matsuura <matsuura.yuki.200095@gmail.com>
Description: Estimates extended two-way fixed-effects difference-in-differences
    models for staggered interventions following Wooldridge (2021)
    <doi:10.2139/ssrn.3906345>. Supports flexible treatment-effect
    heterogeneity, anticipation, covariates, continuous treatment intensity,
    correlated random effects, panel corrections, and linear or nonlinear
    response models following Wooldridge (2023) <doi:10.1093/ectj/utad016>.
